<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="Slide_Show_Plugin">  Slide Show Plugin </h1>
<p class='p'>Create web based presentations based on topics with headings</p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"><span class="foswikiTocTitle">On this page:</span> <ul>
